Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.50,Default JP,,0,0,0,,輝く命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.50,Default CN,,0,0,0,,闪耀的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.97,Hikari,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\b0}Shiny Luminous
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光の心と光の意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光之心与光之意志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,全てをひとつにするために！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,让一切合而为一吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:53.32,Default JP,,0,0,0,,来るポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:53.32,Default CN,,0,0,0,,来了！
